ward Gando\n|-\n|[[Ifugao]]||[[Ifugao Provincial Board|Board]]||4||4||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||11\n|Jose Gullitiw\n|-\n|[[Ilocos Norte]]||[[Ilocos Norte Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Eugenio Angelo Barba\n|-\n|[[Ilocos Sur]]||[[Ilocos Sur Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|[[Jerry Singson]]\n|-\n|[[Iloilo]]||[[Iloilo Provincial Board|Board]]||2||2||2||2||2||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Christine Garin\n|-\n|[[Isabela (province)|Isabela]]||[[Isabela Provincial Board|Board]]||3||2||3||2||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Antonio Albano\n|-\n|[[Kalinga (province)|Kalinga]]||[[Kalinga Provincial Board|Board]]||4||4||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||11\n|James Edduba\n|-\n|[[La Union]]||[[La Union Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Aureo Nisce\n|-\n|[[Laguna (province)|Laguna]]||[[Laguna Provincial Board|Board]]||3||3||2||2||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Katherine Agapay\n|-\n|[[Lanao del Norte]]||[[Lanao del Norte Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Maria Cristina Atay\n|-\n|[[Lanao del Sur]]||[[Lanao del Sur Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Bombit Adiong\n|-\n|[[Leyte (province)|Leyte]]||[[Leyte Provincial Board|Board]]||2||2||2||2||2||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|[[Carlo Loreto]]\n|-\n|[[Maguindanao]]||[[Maguindanao Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Lester Sinsuat\n|-\n|[[Marinduque]]||[[Marinduque Provincial Board|Board]]||4||4||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||11\n|Mark Anthony Se\u00f1o\n|-\n|[[Masbate]]||[[Masbate Provincial Board|Board]]||2||4||4||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Jo Kristine Revil\n|-\n|[[Misamis Occidental]]||[[Misamis Occidental Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Aurora Almonte\n|-\n|[[Misamis Oriental]]||[[Misamis Oriental Provincial Board|Board]]||5||5||  ||  ||  ||  || \n|  ||3||13\n|Jose Mari Pelaez\n|-\n|[[Mountain Province]]||[[Mountain Province Provincial Board|Board]]||4||4||  |